Subject: Amazon Workspaces Fail to load with DPI Enabled
Description:
Hi,
We have received reports and were able to reproduce an error.
With DPI Enabled we are not able to use the Amazon Workspaces client.
Please find attached a video showing the issue and the logs collected.
